<div class="splash">
  <h1><strong>BGM's Website <small><code>bgm.cl</code></small></strong></h1>
  <hr class="mt-1"/>

  <p>
    Hey! I'm BGM or B, a Software Developer from Chile! This is my personal website, which also happens to be
    a forum!.
  </p>

  <p>
    This site is a bit of an experiment. I had always wondered whether I wanted to create a portfolio website for my
    projects and articles, but I didn't want it to be static, so I decided to create a website
    where I can keep everything together, and at the same time allow anybody in to share their thoughts at!
  </p>

  <div class="projects">
    <% if Project.any? %>
      <h3>Personal Projects</h3>
      <hr class="mt-1"/>

      <div class="row">
        <% @projects.each do |p| %>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="project-splash">
              <div class="project-title">
                <%= p.name %>
              </div>
              <div class="project-tags">
                <% p.tags.each do |t| %>
                  <div class="project-tag">
                    <%= render :partial => 'tags/tag', :locals => { :tag => t } %>
                  </div>
                <% end %>
              </div>
              <div class="project-description">
                <%= truncate_string(render_pretty(p.long_desc), 350) %>
              </div>
              <div class="project-read-more">
                <%= link_to 'Read More', p, :class =>  'btn btn-sm btn-primary' %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <br/>
      <%= paginate @projects %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
